@startuml
title Timebox 1 - Student Registration Process

actor Staff as "Staff/Admin"

participant "User" as User
participant "Student" as Student

Staff -> User: Register user\n(name, email, password)
User -> User: Validate fields\n& email uniqueness
User -> User: Hash password
User -> User: Assign role = student
User --> Staff: Confirm user created\n(userId)

Staff -> Student: Register student profile\n(userId, personal details)
Student -> Student: Validate email/phone\nDOB, gender, status
Student -> Student: Generate student_no\n(if not provided)
Student -> Student: Store photo & documents
Student --> Staff: Confirm student registered\n(student_no)

@enduml